Package ScheduleModel

Class Student

  • Object
    • ScheduleModel.Student
  • public class Student
extends Object
    This class describes a person (a Student) with the properties of his or her:
         • Name
         • VIAID (unique ID, can't be the same for multiple students)
         • the name of the Class that he or she attends
         • the project group which he or she is being part of
